{"tid":1611902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動po | 毛澤東：工人階級必須領導一切","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:47:56.000Z","uid":200062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4423ce43b40d2a50e7eebb28d13b6bf009859343","tid":1611902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"十一國慶之時，強國七十大壽，係時候響應偉大領袖毛澤東同志嘅呼籲，工人階級站起來，全面深化籌組工會，堅定落實對工聯會嘅取締，遏止工聯會再係工人問題上面說三道四，全面展開對香港權貴資本階級嘅鬥爭，最終目標為建設香港工人命運共同體，邁向新時代香港特色工人攬炒時代<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>組工會啦喂 全港無產階級站起來</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif